highlights.text: “Stargazing” by Kygo and Justin Jesso is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #71.
“Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 40 weeks straight.
Ozuna has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Se Preparó” is the highest at #55.
“Plain Jane” by A$AP Ferg is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 49 spots at #145.
